features: Out Printed Sheet Mask is the perfect skin prep before applying makeup ahead of a girls night out.
Helps brighten your skin complexion and boosts hydration.
Soothing Oat Peptide and ultra-hydrating peach extract.
description: Product Description Going out out? Our Face Facts Girls Night Out Printed Sheet Mask is the perfect skin prep before applying makeup. Packed with Peach Extract, Oat Peptide and Trehalose, this mask boosts skin hydration and brightens your complexion. The perfect pre-party prep! Vegan Friendly Ingredients Aqua, Glycerin, Butylene Glycol, Avena Sativa (Oat) Peptide, Prunus Persica (Peach) Resin Extract, Prunus Persica (Peach) Fruit Extract, Acetyl Hexapeptide-8, Yeast Ferment Extract, Betaine, Trehalose, Sodium Hyaluronate, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Hydroxyacetophenone, Phenoxyethanol, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Allantoin, Chlorphenesin, Parfum, Triethanolamine, Xanthan Gum, 1,2-Hexanediol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Caprylyl Glycol. Directions Thoroughly cleanse and dry the face. Remove the mask from the foil sachet. Use within 15 minutes of opening. Apply the mask over the face ensuring it's smoothed out over the skin. Leave the mask for 20 to 30 minutes then remove by peeling away from the edges. See more
